datasets.name: dataset_19
queryLines: SELECT Home_Tile AS Home_Tile, SUM(Unique_Interstitial_Secondary_Button_Clicks) AS Total_Unique_Interstitial_Secondary_Button_Clicks, SUM(Unique_Interstitial_Views) AS Total_Unique_Interstitial_Views, (SUM(Unique_Interstitial_Secondary_Button_Clicks) / SUM(Unique_Interstitial_Views)) AS Secondary_CTR FROM hpx_events_model_homepage_summary GROUP BY Home_Tile ORDER BY Secondary_CTR DESC
